winrs -r:PCNAME cmd

You have to set it up first in your client pc with

winrm quickconfig


You can also use ssh within windows server to control your other pc's

another way to do that is to download 'psexec' tools (you will find it in the official microsoft website)

then connect to your machine with:

psexec \\MYMACHINE cmd.exe


Remember that when you download psexec you need to move your workign directory with cd to the folder
in which psexec is located
